<p>выдаст тип данных</p>

<p><em>В Ruby всё - объект</em></p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>string - <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">2</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>fixnum - <span style="color:#00D">2</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>float - <span style="color:#60E">2.1</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>array - [...]
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>hash - {...}
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>bignum - <span style="color:#00D">2</span>^<span style="color:#00D">30</span>+<span style="color:#00D">1</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

