<h2 id="урок-6">Урок 6</h2>

<h4 id="блоки">Блоки:</h4>

<p>Стиль принятый для однострочника:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.times { puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Foo!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> }
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Другой синтаксис с несколькими командами:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.times <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Foo!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Bar!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.times { |i| puts i }
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.times <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |i|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Foo!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="счёт-не-с-нуля">Счёт не с нуля:</h3>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#777"># от 10 до 20</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.upto(<span style="color:#00D">20</span>) { |i| puts i }
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="color:#777"># от 20 до 10</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span><span style="color:#00D">20</span>.downto(<span style="color:#00D">10</span>) { |i| puts i }
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span><span style="color:#777"># OR:</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.upto(<span style="color:#00D">20</span>) <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |i|
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>  p i
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span><span style="color:#00D">20</span>.downto(<span style="color:#00D">10</span>) <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |i|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>  p i
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>Решение задания:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#777"># программа делает от 10 до 20 запусков и выводит Foo это количество раз</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#00D">10</span>.upto(<span style="color:#00D">20</span>) <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |x|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  <span style="color:#00D">1</span>.upto(x) { |i| p <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>i<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#D20"> Foo!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> }
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>Rand Charset:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#00D">30</span>.times { print rand(<span style="color:#00D">70</span>..<span style="color:#00D">120</span>).chr }
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Homework:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w(</span><span style="color:#D20">t e r m i n a t o r</span><span style="color:#710">)</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>dash = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">-</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
