<h2 id="урок-7">Урок 7</h2>

<p>Выход из программы:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>a = <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> a == <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Выйти из программы? (Y/N): </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  answer = gets.strip.capitalize
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> answer == <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Y</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>    a = <span style="color:#069">false</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>== - равно
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>!= - не равно
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>&lt;&gt;
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>&gt;=
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>&lt;=
</pre></div>
</div>
