<h2 id="урок-8">Урок 8</h2>

<p>Ruby понимает 10_000_000 как 10 млн.</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>a = <span style="color:#00D">10_000</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Обрывает работу оператора:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">break</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Hello</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>.reverse
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Ranges:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>(<span style="color:#00D">1</span>..<span style="color:#00D">10</span>).each { |x| puts x*<span style="color:#00D">4</span> }
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>(<span style="color:#00D">1</span>..<span style="color:#00D">5</span>).each =&gt; <span style="color:#00D">1</span> <span style="color:#00D">2</span> <span style="color:#00D">3</span> <span style="color:#00D">4</span> <span style="color:#00D">5</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>(<span style="color:#00D">1</span>...<span style="color:#00D">5</span>).each =&gt; <span style="color:#00D">1</span> <span style="color:#00D">2</span> <span style="color:#00D">3</span> <span style="color:#00D">4</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="color:#777"># можно не только цифры:</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>(<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">aa</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>..<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">ff</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>).each { |x| puts x }
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>(<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">10aa</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>..<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">20ff</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>).each { |x| puts x }
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>GUI framework:
<a href="http://shoesrb.com/">Shoes! The easiest little GUI toolkit, for Ruby.</a></p>

<h2 id="урок-9">Урок 9</h2>

<h3 id="методы">Методы</h3>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">foo</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Методу можно передать какой-либо параметр, и он вернёт какое-либо значение.</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">gets_password</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Введите пароль: </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">return</span> gets.chomp
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>xx = gets_password
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Был введён пароль </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>xx<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>return - можно не писать</p>

<p>По умолчанию руби возвращает результат последнего выражения.</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">print_name</span> name
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Hello </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>name<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>print_name <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Alex</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Внутри метода все переменые определяются заново (локальные переменные метода)</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>a = <span style="color:#00D">1</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">foo</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  a = <span style="color:#00D">2</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>puts a <span style="color:#777"># =&gt; 1</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>@a - переменная экземпляра</p>

<h3 id="объекты-экземпляры-класса-instance">Объекты, экземпляры класса (instance)</h3>

<p>“foo”
“foo”
находятся в разных участках памяти, это разные объекты. Чтобы закрепить за одним участком используются <em>символы</em>.</p>

<h4 id="символы-symbol">Символы (symbol):</h4>

<p>Обозначается как:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#A60">:foo</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Можно переменным назначать значение символов.</p>

<p>true or false:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">aaa</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> == <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">aaa</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>puts <span style="color:#A60">:aaa</span> == <span style="color:#A60">:aaa</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">aaa</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>.equal? <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">aaa</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> <span style="color:#777"># false</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>puts <span style="color:#A60">:aaa</span>.equal? <span style="color:#A60">:aaa</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>.equal? - сравнивает объекты по ссылке</p>

<h4 id="проверка-id-объекта">Проверка id объекта:</h4>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">aaa</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>.object_id <span style="color:#777"># каждый раз меняется</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#A60">:aaa</span>.object_id <span style="color:#777"># у символа один и тот же</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="массивы-arrays">Массивы (arrays)</h3>

<p><a href="https://ruby-doc.org/core-2.5.1/Array.html">Class: Array (Ruby 2.5.1)</a></p>

<p>Массив = набор объектов</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = []
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>arr2 = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w{</span><span style="color:#D20">foo bar zoo moo faf</span><span style="color:#710">}</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>arr &lt;&lt; <span style="color:#00D">14</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>arr &lt;&lt; <span style="color:#00D">22</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h2 id="урок-10">Урок 10</h2>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">movie</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  action = [<span style="color:#A60">:left</span>, <span style="color:#A60">:right</span>, <span style="color:#A60">:up</span>, <span style="color:#A60">:down</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  x = rand(<span style="color:#00D">0</span>..<span style="color:#00D">3</span>)
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">return</span> action[x]
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">say</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>  sleep <span style="color:#60E">0.06</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>  speech = movie
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Go to </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>speech<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>  sleep <span style="color:#60E">0.4</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>capitalize every name:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w{</span><span style="color:#D20">joe matt mary olga oleg peter vasya</span><span style="color:#710">}</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>arr.each <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |x|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  puts x.capitalize
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>индекс arr[2]</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = [<span style="color:#00D">1</span>, <span style="color:#00D">2</span>, <span style="color:#00D">3</span>, <span style="color:#00D">4</span>, <span style="color:#00D">5</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>arr2 = arr[<span style="color:#00D">1</span>..<span style="color:#00D">3</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>puts arr2 <span style="color:#777">#=&gt; 2 3 4</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w{</span><span style="color:#D20">aa bb cc dd ee</span><span style="color:#710">}</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>arr[<span style="color:#00D">1</span>..<span style="color:#00D">3</span>][<span style="color:#00D">2</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#777">#=&gt; &quot;dd&quot;</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h4 id="удаление-элемента-из-массива">Удаление элемента из массива</h4>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = [<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">aa</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">bb</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">cc</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">dd</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>]
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>arr.delete_at <span style="color:#00D">1</span> <span style="color:#777"># delete &quot;bb&quot;</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>arr.delete <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">dd</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> <span style="color:#777"># delete &quot;dd&quot;</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>Удаление из массива (задача):</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>person = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w{</span><span style="color:#D20">vasiliy mariya joe bob marley</span><span style="color:#710">}</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>  person.size.times <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |x|
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>    puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>x<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#D20">. </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>person[x].capitalize<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Кого удалить? (порядковый номер): </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>  del = gets.to_i
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>  person.delete_at del
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">=====</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Или вариант с each</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>person = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w{</span><span style="color:#D20">vasiliy mariya joe bob marley</span><span style="color:#710">}</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  i = <span style="color:#00D">0</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>  person.each <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |x|
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>    puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>i<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#D20">. </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>x.capitalize<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>    i += <span style="color:#00D">1</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Кого удалить? (порядковый номер): </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>  del = gets.to_i
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>  person.delete_at del
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">=====</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n18" name="n18">18</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>Добавление в массив с выводом на экран:</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = []
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Enter name to add: </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>  name = gets.strip.capitalize
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> name == <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">break</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>  arr &lt;&lt; name
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">===</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>  x = <span style="color:#00D">0</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span>  arr.each <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |name|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n18" name="n18">18</a></span>    puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>x<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#D20">. </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>name<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n19" name="n19">19</a></span>    x += <span style="color:#00D">1</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n20" name="n20">20</a></strong></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n21" name="n21">21</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n22" name="n22">22</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
