<h2 id="урок-11">Урок 11</h2>

<h4 id="поменять-значения-местами">Поменять значения местами</h4>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>a = <span style="color:#00D">50</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>b = <span style="color:#00D">20</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>a, b = b, a
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>puts a
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>puts b
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>var 2:</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>a = a + b
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>b = a - b
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>a = a - b
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="обработка-двумерного-массива">Обработка двумерного массива:</h3>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = [ [<span style="color:#00D">1</span>, <span style="color:#00D">2</span>], [<span style="color:#00D">3</span>, <span style="color:#00D">4</span>], [<span style="color:#00D">5</span>, <span style="color:#00D">6</span>] ]
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>arr.each <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |item|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  item.each <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |x|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>    puts x
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h3 id="each_with_index---метод-заменяющий-что-делали-выше-на-прошлых-уроках">.each_with_index - метод заменяющий, что делали выше на прошлых уроках:</h3>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>arr = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">%w{</span><span style="color:#D20"> Vova Masha Petya Alisha </span><span style="color:#710">}</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>arr.each_with_index <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |item, i|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>i<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#D20"> </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>item<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h3 id="хеши-hash">Хеши (Hash):</h3>

<p>Это структура данных
Key value storage - хранилище ключ значение
В других языках ещё называют Dictionary</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>hash = <span style="color:#036;font-weight:bold">Hash</span>.new
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>hash = {}
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>hash = { <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Mike</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">3538300</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>,
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>        <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Jessie</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">4348829</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>}
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>puts hash[<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Mike</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>]
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<blockquote>
  <p>=&gt; называется Hash Rocket</p>
</blockquote>

<h4 id="используй-одинарные-кавычки-а-двойные-для-интерполяции">Используй одинарные кавычки, а двойные для интерполяции.</h4>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>a = <span style="color:#00D">2</span>+<span style="color:#00D">2</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>a<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> <span style="color:#777">#=&gt; 4</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">#{a}</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> <span style="color:#777">#=&gt; #{a}</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>options = {
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  <span style="color:#A60">:font_size</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#00D">10</span>,
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  <span style="color:#A60">:font_family</span> =&gt; <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Arial</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>,
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  <span style="color:#A60">:arr</span> =&gt; [<span style="color:#00D">1</span>, <span style="color:#00D">5</span>, <span style="color:#00D">8</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>  }
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>options[<span style="color:#A60">:font_size</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>options[<span style="color:#A60">:font_family</span>]
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>options[<span style="color:#A60">:arr</span>][<span style="color:#00D">2</span>]
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<blockquote>
  <p>для исследования используй .inspect и .class</p>
</blockquote>

<h4 id="обращение-к-хешу-по-ключу-и-получаем-значение">Обращение к хешу по ключу и получаем значение</h4>

<h3 id="добавление-элемента-в-хеш">Добавление элемента в хеш:</h3>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>hash = {}
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>hash[<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Alisha</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>] = <span style="color:#00D">636400</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>hash[<span style="color:#A60">:foo</span>] = <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Bar</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 id="решение-задания-телефонная-книга">Решение задания “Телефонная книга”</h4>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#777"># Enter name (Enter to stop):</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#777"># Enter phone number:</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#777"># add to hash</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>phonebook = {}
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Enter name (Enter to stop): </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>  name = gets.strip.capitalize
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> name == <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">break</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Enter phone number: </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>  number = gets.strip
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n18" name="n18">18</a></span>  phonebook[name] = number
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n19" name="n19">19</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n20" name="n20">20</a></strong></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n21" name="n21">21</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">=== My Phone Book ===</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n22" name="n22">22</a></span>phonebook.each <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |name, phone|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n23" name="n23">23</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>name<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#D20"> number is </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>phone<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n24" name="n24">24</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n25" name="n25">25</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">=====================</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h5 id="важное-замечание-в-хеше-через-each-элементы-могут-выводиться-не-по-порядку-хеш-не-предназначен-для-хранения-элементов-по-порядку-в-отличие-от-массива">Важное замечание: в хеше через each элементы могут выводиться не по порядку. Хеш не предназначен для хранения элементов по порядку, в отличие от массива.</h5>

<h4 id="вызвать-нужный-элемент-из-хеша">Вызвать нужный элемент из хеша:</h4>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>phonebook[<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">Alisha</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>]
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h4 id="решение-задачи-англо-русский-переводчик">Решение задачи “Англо-русский переводчик”:</h4>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>words = {
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">dog</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">собака</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>,
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">cat</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">кошка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>,
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">frog</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">лягушка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>  }
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> <span style="color:#069">true</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>  print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Введите слово: </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>  user_word = gets.strip.downcase
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> user_word == <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">break</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Перевод: </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>words[user_word]<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>  puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<blockquote>
  <p>У слова может быть несколько переводов, поэтому можно переписать программу, где значение хеша = массив.</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>fruits = []
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>fruits &lt;&lt; {<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">name</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>=&gt;<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">banana</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">cost</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>=&gt;<span style="color:#00D">10</span>} &lt;&lt; {<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">name</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>=&gt;<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">apple</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">cost</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>=&gt;<span style="color:#00D">7</span>}
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#777">#=&gt; [{&quot;name&quot;=&gt;&quot;banana&quot;, &quot;cost&quot;=&gt;10}, {&quot;name&quot;=&gt;&quot;apple&quot;, &quot;cost&quot;=&gt;7}]</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<h2 id="урок-12">Урок 12</h2>

<h4 id="перечисление-ключей-и-значений-хеша">Перечисление ключей и значений хеша:</h4>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>hash = { <span style="color:#606">right</span>: <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Right</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="color:#606">left</span>: <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Left</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="color:#606">top</span>: <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Top</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="color:#606">down</span>: <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Down</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> }
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>puts hash.keys
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>puts hash.values
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span><span style="color:#777"># ИЛИ</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>hash.each_key <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |key|
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>  puts key
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>hash.each_value <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">do</span> |value|
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>  puts value
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>hash.keys и hash.values - это массивы, к ним можно применять методы .size и т.п.</p>

<h4 id="задание-посчитать-количество-переводов">Задание: посчитать количество переводов</h4>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>words = {
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">dog</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; [<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">собака</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">шавка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">бобик</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>],
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">cat</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; [<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">кошка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">кошечка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>],
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">frog</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; [<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">лягушка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">квакушка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>],
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>  <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">mouse</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span> =&gt; [<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">мышь</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">мышка</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>]
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>}
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>result = <span style="color:#00D">0</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span>words.each_value { |value| result += value.size }
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">All words: </span><span style="background-color:hsla(0,0%,0%,0.07);color:black"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">#{</span>result<span style="font-weight:bold;color:#666">}</span></span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 id="проверка-наличия-ключа-в-хеше">Проверка наличия ключа в хеше:</h4>
