<h4 id="attr_reader---делает-переменную-доступную-для-чтения">attr_reader - делает переменную доступную для чтения:</h4>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">def</span> <span style="color:#06B;font-weight:bold">last_person</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  <span style="color:#33B">@last_person</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span><span style="color:#777"># заменяется на:</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>attr_reader <span style="color:#A60">:last_person</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
